    "key_finding": "All 61 raw citations across 24 concepts decompose into 57 self-referential (concept-inventor domain) + 4 F-INV2-downstream (seeded injection domains). Zero independent organic citations exist. The concept-inventor domain is a closed self-referential loop: it invents concepts, cites them in audit lessons, which inflate raw counts, which justify more invention. vocabulary-ceiling reached 11 raw citations (highest of any concept) while having 0 organic — a pure Goodhart artifact where the metric hit near-threshold via self-referential inflation alone.",
